// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0669 — Mass File Rename (safepay)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9d9ce38f-abab-59b5-9132-1fad59335bec

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
